OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A leading whisky expert is still living
OL,6, in lockdown because he fears losing his
OL,7, senses and his livelihood to Covid.    
OL,9,FSince March 2020 Blair Bowman has only 
OL,10,Fventured out of his Edinburgh home for 
OL,11,Fwalks and to collect his weekly shop.  
OL,13,FBefore the pandemic he travelled the   
OL,14,Fworld for corporate events, but now    
OL,15,Fdoes all his work online - and his     
OL,16,Fbusiness is booming.                   
OL,18,FMr Bowman told BBC Radio Scotland's    
OL,19,FMornings programme: "At the moment the 
OL,20,Frisks are just much too high for me."  
